reviewText: Great grift for my dad, loved to watch these western shows was he was younger and it really brought back memories for him.

They bring back a lot of memories. A lot of the plots are ridiculous and the dialog? . . . well . . . I guess a good word to use is "corny".  But still . . . I enjoy every minute of them. If for no other reason these westerns bring home how innocent we all were when the westerns were originally produced/shown.
